{"tid":1936291,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陳法拉被二創舊作寸爆","createTime":"2020-03-21T06:52:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T10:54:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"15c311b8a86bfe86c4e72eed4ea7beac7e13062d","tid":1936291,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T06:52:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200321/7RERLXQNP5G7SG3Y6CVTI4VV4E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200321%2F7RERLXQNP5G7SG3Y6CVTI4VV4E%2F&d=KoefzaQlkmro%2FPgOzv92F%2BDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=dd6ed02b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200321%2F7RERLXQNP5G7SG3Y6CVTI4VV4E%2F&h=fd203589\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200321/7RERLXQNP5G7SG3Y6CVTI4VV4E/</a><br />\n<br />\n陳法拉被二創舊作寸爆<br />\n<br />\n四川出生、擁美國護照的陳法拉日前在網上炮轟美國總統特朗普（Donald Trump）「Chinese Virus」論是種族歧視，遭網民圍插，作家王迪詩更寸她應放棄美國籍表愛國心，事後法拉在社交網發禪文反擊。<br />\n<br />\n有網媒fb專頁前晚將法拉2013年主演的劇集《衝上雲霄II》重新配音，片中副機長翟威廉與同事商量食雲南米線，法拉演的Holiday鬧對方歧視雲南人，提議應叫「新型米線」，翟威廉反問︰「之後再有新嘅米線叫乜嘢好？新新型米線、真點新型米線、新型米線plus？」而該段二創短片又講述法拉回家再被吳鎮宇寸爆︰「大阪燒、德國鹹豬手、基輔雞扒個個都咁叫，你唔係身有屎，點會覺得人哋歧視你。」<br />\n<br />\n撰文︰祖李<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200321/large/1584711120_c54d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200321%2Flarge%2F1584711120_c54d.jpg&h=b22d5670&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳法拉的舊作《衝上雲霄II》被二創重新配音，寸爆法拉維護內地政權。互聯網圖片"},{"pid":"5b588d6e62314dc75b55aabddaef2d75e3044737","tid":1936291,"uid":174441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15c311b8a86bfe86c4e72eed4ea7beac7e13062d","tid":1936291,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T06:52:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.co